\begin_layout Section
Discussion
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
While there were some difficulties with this lab,
 this had significantly less issues setting up and diagnosing problems,
 but there were still humps in the way.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
CCS project issues:
 After just accepting the issues that comes with editing projects,
 not touching the structure itself but putting different main/additional files fixed any building issues.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Hardware issues:
 We found during the implementation of a couple pins on the MCU's that the Pin03 on one of them was broken off.
 We rectified it by just simply using the female header underneath.
 We also purchased USB-C to Micro-USB cables,
 so it effectively solved any remaining hardware issues in connecting to the laptop.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Header Issues:
 For some reason the timer code was stuck in Milliseconds while our code ran in microseconds,
 so we had to edit the headers themselves to fix the issue.
\end_layout

